This project builds on:
- SmolLM3-3B-Base (HuggingFaceTB) — base model.
- ngspice — circuit simulator (used as the verifiable reward).
- AnalogCoder — external evaluation benchmark (evaluation only; never used in training).

Training data is drawn only from openly licensed sources (Apache-2.0, MIT, BSD,
CC-BY / CC-BY-SA / CC-BY-NC / CC-BY-NC-SA, CC0, public domain). Released model
weights are licensed CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0 (research / educational use).
